The '''''Adventures of a Jedi Prince''''' series, also known as '''''The Glove of Darth Vader'' series''' or simply the '''''Jedi Prince''''' series, is a [[Star Wars Legends|Legends]] junior novel series from authors [[Paul Davids]] and [[Hollace Davids]]. It includes six volumes that were published by [[Bantam Spectra|Bantam Skylark]] in paperback from [[1992]] to [[1993]]. The complete series was reprinted in the [[1997]] hardcover collections ''[[Star Wars: Book One]]'' and ''[[Star Wars: Book Two]]''.

The series chronicles the story of [[Ken]], a twelve-year-old [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitive]] boy, and his adventures in the time after [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']]. Many elements from the series have been widely disregarded by the Expanded Universe.

